# GitHub Actions Notes

Workflow
A YAML file that defines automation.

Event
The event that triggers a workflow.

Job
A group of steps executed on a runner.

Step
An individual command or action.

Runner
The machine that executes the job.

Artifact
A file generated by a workflow.

CI
Continuous Integration.

CD
Continuous Delivery or Deployment.

Secret
Sensitive data stored securely in GitHub.
